{"tid":550741,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] [Zelda:BotW] 薩爾達傳說:曠野之息 (15) 2018年初更新中文字幕","createTime":"2018-02-05T04:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T16:00:45.000Z","uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15821834715f8607ca0cee6da5027bb6429b92db","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">薩爾達傳說: 曠野之息</span></strong></span><br />\n預定2018年初透過<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遊戲更新</strong></span>支援繁體中文<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_zelda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_zelda.png&h=3046d42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">來自「薩爾達傳說」製作人青沼先生的訊息</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5mftsnuV9o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do5mftsnuV9o&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fdc0976d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5mftsnuV9o</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.劇透討論(<span style=\"color: orange;\">同劇情內容有關嘅討論/Screencap</span>)<br />\n請用粉色細字&amp;post圖link</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.此遊戲為ARPG，需閱讀對話及系統信息，唔係實卡關</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.發問前睇下Q&amp;A先</strong></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d4672aec34892d4a7d6d3a0b51e605b8eb51a48e","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:43:59.000Z","msg":"Q: 有無得開多個Save?<br />\nA: Save跟Switch嘅profile, 開game嗰陣揀另一個profile就得<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無得隨時轉英/日文?<br />\nA: 有,入Switch setting轉語言就得<br />\n<br />\nQ: 一開始拎完地圖要做乜?<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">解附近嗰四個神社(Shrine)</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 雪山點上?<br />\nA: 手持火把/整+食防寒食物(煮過嘅Spicy Peppers)/著防寒裝<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點拎防寒裝?<br />\nA: 三種方法:<br />\n1)去Great Plateau南面呀伯間屋有個食譜,跟住黎煮俾佢食就得<br />\n2)拎完飛行器去Great Plateau南面呀伯間屋<br />\n3)上雪山頂位揾呀伯<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點煮野食?<br />\nA: 有啲火堆上面有個爐, hold住食材行埋去撳A就有得煮<br />\n<br />\nQ: 解完任去邊揾呀伯?<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">四個Shrine交叉點</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 做完XXX唔知點好<br />\nA: 周圍行下實有野做 依隻game係真係open world 無限你一定要做乜唔做乜<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解入唔到沙漠城<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為你有J</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 點睇進度?<br />\nA: 爆機後地圖左下角<br />\n<br />\nQ: 爆完機仲有無得繼續玩?<br />\nA: 有, 會load返打final boss前個save, 個save file會多粒星<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點睇玩左幾多個鐘?<br />\nA: 入Switch主頁click自己個icon可以睇到自己各遊戲遊玩時間<br />\n(第一次開隻game 10日之後先會出現, 個時間係round down去最近嘅5小時)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點採礦?<br />\nA: 用hammer '攻擊'佢/ 用炸彈炸佢(注意啲礦石會飛到周圍都係) <br />\n<br />\nQ: 血月除左怪重生仲有乜特別?<br />\nA: 當晚煮野食會有bonus效果<br />\n<br />\nTips:<br />\n1)唔慣用X跳可以入setting轉用B跳<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2)解迷卡關時不妨諗下自己有咩能力同埋睇下一入去個牌有咩提示</span><br />\n3)冰能力除左結冰仲可以解冰 <br />\n4)善用地圖個貼紙功能mark低邊度有特別素材/礦之類<br />\n5)拎到相機後見到乜都影下儲圖鑑+可以用sensor搵野<br />\n6)Guardian啲炮可以盾ZL+A反射<br />\n7)唔夠打咪Skip住先囉<br />\n8)如果唔知個道具/材料有咩用可以留意下佢嘅description<br />\n9)更新v1.2.0後可以入game setting轉語音語言"},{"pid":"66351a530b088477a10e3a1b5b178c769fb1cf07","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">DLC Pack 1 - <span style=\"color: orange;\">已出</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DDvo08VXYAQgDRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDDvo08VXYAQgDRq.jpg&h=39b89a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細介紹<br />\n<a href=\"http://zelda.com/breath-of-the-wild/news/expansion-pass-dlc-pack-1-detailed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzelda.com%2Fbreath-of-the-wild%2Fnews%2Fexpansion-pass-dlc-pack-1-detailed%2F&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=935e003e\" target=\"_blank\">http://zelda.com/breath-of-the-wild/news/expansion-pass-dlc-pack-1-detailed/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C-yMitcXcAAShze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC-yMitcXcAAShze.jpg&h=fd0e50ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://zelda.com/breath-of-the-wild/assets/img/news-articles/18/05_tinglesoutfit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzelda.com%2Fbreath-of-the-wild%2Fassets%2Fimg%2Fnews-articles%2F18%2F05_tinglesoutfit.jpg&h=740284d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topics.nintendo.co.jp/export/sites/nintendo_topics/images/article_img/00000625_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopics.nintendo.co.jp%2Fexport%2Fsites%2Fnintendo_topics%2Fimages%2Farticle_img%2F00000625_03.jpg&h=4250d6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topics.nintendo.co.jp/export/sites/nintendo_topics/images/article_img/00000625_13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopics.nintendo.co.jp%2Fexport%2Fsites%2Fnintendo_topics%2Fimages%2Farticle_img%2F00000625_13.jpg&h=552bc2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n~大師劍試練<br />\n~足跡回顧mode<br />\n~困難模式<br />\n~新裝<br />\n~Yahaha Sensor"},{"pid":"b9d7a517f9b680683302ca2b0f2dec167e9ade05","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">DLC Pack 2 - <span style=\"color: orange;\">2017年冬</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DCNsoZjVwAEdTaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDCNsoZjVwAEdTaW.jpg&h=25fc508f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n敬請期待!"},{"pid":"6c6f06a50e47bedffe8e2bec8e95e666f7b94666","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"使用Amiibo可換取相應道具<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Ng776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNg776.jpg&h=9775509b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/071237_ea903ed5a1a679a63fad09f0f4dad568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F071237_ea903ed5a1a679a63fad09f0f4dad568.jpg&h=685cf97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/071250_25ba35b034bb4b252a3d7274b0174212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F071250_25ba35b034bb4b252a3d7274b0174212.jpg&h=22762c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/071302_c1cfd0a4ece87e5c27445b3095e03432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F071302_c1cfd0a4ece87e5c27445b3095e03432.jpg&h=73ed4fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/071313_2e818de69ba2bbdd98af637b0028b0a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F071313_2e818de69ba2bbdd98af637b0028b0a6.jpg&h=d16219ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAmiibo一覽<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/amiibo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Famiibo%2F&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6591ac7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/amiibo/</a>"},{"pid":"0fd285609537a9e1ed8fd64c9d5e46ed595ecb28","tid":550741,"uid":60074,"like":0,"d